00:23:28,800 --> 00:23:30,860
 That's great that it is.

353
00:23:30,860 --> 00:23:33,420
 It's a byproduct of the truth.

354
00:23:33,420 --> 00:23:37,660
 But we're here because this is real, because God is real.

355
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:41,220
 He really exists.

356
00:23:41,220 --> 00:23:43,580
 He's really there.

357
00:23:43,580 --> 00:23:48,220
 And that's the foundation of why we're here, because God is there.

