00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:09,480
 We're not just here because we don't know what else to do on Sunday morning.

391
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:11,820
 We're here because God loves us.

392
00:26:11,820 --> 00:26:12,820
 He loves you.

393
00:26:12,820 --> 00:26:13,820
 He loves me.

394
00:26:13,820 --> 00:26:15,640
 We're objects of His love.

395
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:17,480
 And that's why we show up.

396
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:21,380
 That's why we're here.

